8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "node_memory_usage_rate", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "在分析过程中发现以下异常调用链和日志关键词：\n\n### 日志关键词提取:\n1. **反射异常**: 多个日志条目报告出现 `InvocationTargetException`。\n2. **Byteman Agent 错误**: 出现多个 `Agent failed to start` 和 `attempting to load Byteman agent more than once` 错误。\n3. **内存相关警告**: 日志提到 `gc` 和 `GCHelper`。\n4. **请求上下文超时**: Frontend 服务报告 `context deadline exceeded`。\n\n### 诺基亚异常故障分析:\n1. **异常**: `InvocationTargetException`\n   - **组件**: adservice\n   - **原因**: 此异常通常表明反射调用失败，可能与代码或环境配置问题有关。\n   - **证据**: `\"Exception in thread \"\"Attach Listener\"\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\"`\n\n2. **异常**: Byteman agent 加载问题\n   - **组件**: adservice\n   - **原因**: 多次尝试加载 Byteman agent 失败，可能导致服务的不稳定。\n   - **证据**: `\"Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"`\n\n3. **异常**: GC 调用\n   - **组件**: adservice\n   - **原因**: AdService 尝试触发 GC 相关操作可能导致资源崩溃。\n   - **证据**: `\"byteman gc helper trigger gc\"`\n\n4. **异常**: 请求超时\n   - **组件**: frontend\n   - **原因**: Frontend 在获取广告时超时，可能受到后台服务延迟的影响。\n   - **证据**: `\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"`\n\n### 检测到的错误关键词\n- `InvocationTargetException`\n- `Agent failed to start`\n- `attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`\n- `gc`\n- `GCHelper`\n- `context deadline exceeded`\n\n### JSON输出:\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"InvocationTargetException\", \"Agent failed to start\", \"attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\", \"gc\", \"GCHelper\", \"context deadline exceeded\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"反射调用失败\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Exception in thread \\\"\\\"Attach Listener\\\"\\\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent 安装失败\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"GC 调用导致资源问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"byteman gc helper trigger gc\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"请求广告超时\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n``` \n\n以上是对日志数据的分析结果。如果需要进一步的细节分析或者处理建议，请提供相关请求。", "metric_analysis_findings": "已从指标数据中发现以下显著变化的异常指标：\n\n1. **Node 异常**:\n   - Node `aiops-k8s-04`: `node_memory_usage_rate` 显著增加。\n   - Node `aiops-k8s-08`: `redis-cart-0` Pod 的 `pod_cpu_usage` 显著增加。\n\n2. **Service 异常**:\n   - `cartservice-1`: `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 在故障期间达到了 19.55 的显著上升。\n   - `currencyservice-1`: `rrt_max` 在故障期间显著增加，达到了 90984.28。\n   - `adservice-0`: 显示 `rrt_max` 和 `client_error_ratio` 异常变化。\n\n以下是异常检测的初步假说：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node `aiops-k8s-04` 的 `node_memory_usage_rate` 显著增加，可能是系统进程或硬件问题。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: normal_median = 32.29, fault_median = 51.91, median_change_ratio = 0.466\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务 `cartservice-1` 的 `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 显著上升，指示潜在的服务处理错误。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio: normal_p99 = 0.0, fault_p99 = 19.55, p99_change_ratio = 2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"`currencyservice-1` 的 `rrt_max` 显著增加，可能导致服务响应变慢。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: normal_p99 = 10301.6, fault_p99 = 90984.28, p99_change_ratio = 1.5932\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"`redis-cart-0` Pod 的 `pod_cpu_usage` 显著增加，可能指示资源消耗过多。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: normal_p99 = 0.12, fault_p99 = 0.05, p99_change_ratio = 0.7576\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n上述数据和假说为进一步故障分析提供了基础，指出了潜在的资源瓶颈和性能问题区域。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据获取的调用链数据，我对这些调用链进行了分析并找到了几个显著的异常调用链。以下是我的发现和相关分析：\n\n1. **显著延迟**\n   - `checkoutservice` 调用 `checkoutservice` 中的 `EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation`，延迟倍数为 3.3 倍。\n   - `checkoutservice` 调用 `PaymentService/Charge`，延迟倍数为 3.27 倍。\n   - `checkoutservice` 调用 `CartService/EmptyCart`，延迟倍数为 3.65 倍。\n   - `cartservice` 调用 `cartservice` 中的 `GetCart`，延迟达到 19.66 倍。\n   - `frontend` 调用 `AdService/GetAds`，延迟达到 7.47 倍。\n   - `productcatalogservice` 调用 `productcatalogservice` 中的 `ProductCatalogService/ListProducts`，延迟出现几次超过 2 倍。\n\n2. **错误传播**\n   - `frontend` 调用 `frontend` 中 `AdService/GetAds` 时，出现了 \"context deadline exceeded\" 错误，该错误提示可能是上下游服务的响应时间过长或阻塞。\n\n3. **潜在根因定位**\n   - `checkoutservice` 多个内部服务的操作如 `PaymentService/Charge` 和 `EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation` 都表现出高延迟，可能问题根源在此服务。\n   - `cartservice` 中的 `GetCart` 操作也表现出十分高的延迟，需要进一步检查该服务是否有性能瓶颈。\n\n根据以上信息，建议对 `checkoutservice` 和 `cartservice` 展开深入调查，以确认这些服务的高延迟是否是问题根源及其具体原因，尤其是资源消耗或网络问题。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->EmailService\", \"checkoutservice->PaymentService\", \"checkoutservice->CartService\", \"cartservice->cartservice\", \"frontend->AdService\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation 操作出现延迟率 3.3 倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PaymentService/Charge 操作出现延迟率 3.27 倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService/EmptyCart 延迟率 3.65 倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"GetCart 操作延迟率达 19.66 倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用 AdService/GetAds 的延迟达 7.47 倍，并出现错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
